<div class='action-box'>
	<h1 class='title'>Instructions</h1>
	<p>Welcome.</p>

	<p>Start a trial by pressing the space bar. A fixation dot will appear in the middle of the window. Stare at it.
	A short time later (less than a second) a word (RED, GREEN, BLUE, or YELLOW) will appear on the
	screen, and the word will be printed in red, green, blue, or yellow ink.</p>
	
	<p class='bold'>Your task is to classify, as quickly as possible, the ink color, regardless of the word name.</p>
	
	<p>If the ink color is red, press the <span class='italic'>s</span> key; for blue, press the <span class='italic'>f</span> key; for green, press the <span class='italic'>j</span> key, for yellow, press
	the <span class='italic'>l</span> key.</p>
	
	<p>Press the space bar to continue.</p>
</div>

<script type="text/javascript">

$( document ).ready( function() {
	$( document ).keydown( function( event ){ keyPress( event ) } );								
} );

function keyPress( event ) {
	var keyCode = event.which;
	if( keyCode == 32 ) {
		window.location = '<%= full_screen_warning_study_index_path %>';
	}
}

</script>